messages.message:
The logs dashboard received some love recently :slightly_smiling_face: You can now shows context information - you can answer questions like: what stage is this log from, what file does log belong to, etc. This should help with error debugging.
There is also a new download logs button. Customers can use it to just download the logs from the dashboard and share it with us in case they face any issues with their flows.  This is in release-21.3.0 and you can try it on instabase.com (http://instabase.com)
Have a nice weekend :slightly_smiling_face:
